<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>User Profile - Lab 11</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; padding: 20px; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #f4f7f6; }
        nav { background: #2c3e50; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        nav a { color: #ecf0f1; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
        .card { background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .user-info { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 5px solid #3498db; margin: 20px 0; }
        .btn-logout { background: #e74c3c; color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; }
        .btn-logout:hover { background: #c0392b; }
        .badge { background: #d4edda; color: #155724; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <a href="/">🏠 Back to Home</a>
        <span style="color: white;">Logged in as: <%= user.email %></span>
    </nav>

    <div class="card">
        <h1>👤 Private Profile <span class="badge">Protected</span></h1>
        <p>This page is only accessible because you have a valid <strong>JWT Authentication Cookie</strong>.</p>
        
        <div class="user-info">
            <p><strong>Database ID:</strong> <%= user.userId %></p>
            <p><strong>Email Address:</strong> <%= user.email %></p>
        </div>

        <p>Security Check: Your session is active. You can safely sign out below.</p>

        <form method="POST" action="/logout">
            <button type="submit" class="btn-logout">Sign Out / Logout</button>
        </form>
    </div>

</body>
</html>